64
00:05:23,664 --> 00:05:27,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But Boss, Takumi's getting better and better!</b></font>

65
00:05:27,374 --> 00:05:29,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's really incredible! Right?</b></font>

66
00:05:29,574 --> 00:05:34,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You said it. Since entering Project D,
