68
00:05:38,344 --> 00:05:39,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and used to space out all the time.</b></font>

69
00:05:39,784 --> 00:05:43,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Last night, standing off a bit</b></font>

70
00:05:43,454 --> 00:05:46,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and watching Takumi talk like old
friends with Ryosuke Takahashi,</b></font>

71
00:05:46,784 --> 00:05:49,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it made me a little sad.</b></font>

72
00:05:49,524 --> 00:05:53,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Like he'd become someone
