75
00:06:05,104 --> 00:06:06,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ah, it's Takumi!</b></font>

76
00:06:06,744 --> 00:06:09,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Speak of the devil, huh?</b></font>

77
00:06:14,984 --> 00:06:16,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You on your way back from work?</b></font>

78
00:06:16,784 --> 00:06:19,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki had the early shift, so he's already gone.</b></font>

79
00:06:19,324 --> 00:06:21,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, uh...</b></font>

80
00:06:21,454 --> 00:06:26,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's something else, sir. My dad
bought a new car. Did you know?</b></font>

81
00:06:26,764 --> 00:06:29,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, I know. An Impreza, right?</b></font>

82
00:06:29,564 --> 00:06:31,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, so you knew?</b></font>

83
00:06:31,634 --> 00:06:34,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--For real?
--An Impreza?!</b></font>

84
00:06:34,234 --> 00:06:37,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Stupid old man, pissing me off as always!</i></b></font>

85
00:06:37,604 --> 00:06:40,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Why suddenly spring this only on me?</i></b></font>

86
00:06:40,004 --> 00:06:42,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So did you take it for a spin?</b></font>

87
00:06:42,574 --> 00:06:44,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I drove it this morning, yes.</b></font>

88
00:06:44,414 --> 00:06:45,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How was it?</b></font>

89
00:06:45,584 --> 00:06:51,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll tell you how it was. For me,
it was like being in a flying saucer.</b></font>

90
00:06:51,284 --> 00:06:52,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A flying saucer?</b></font>

91
00:06:52,854 --> 00:06:54,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What does that even mean?!</b></font>

92
00:06:54,754 --> 00:06:57,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It had such a powerful impact...</b></font>

93
00:06:57,664 --> 00:07:01,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Up till now, I've driven
without even thinking about it.</b></font>

94
00:07:01,034 --> 00:07:07,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But now, all of a sudden... it's like I don't
know how to drive the Eight-Six anymore.</b></font>

95
00:07:07,174 --> 00:07:09,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hold on now! What's that supposed to mean?</b></font>

96
00:07:09,804 --> 00:07:13,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think you know how to drive
the Eight-Six better than anyone!</b></font>

97
00:07:13,204 --> 00:07:14,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right!</b></font>

98
00:07:14,374 --> 00:07:17,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I... I don't really know how to put it...</b></font>

99
00:07:17,614 --> 00:07:22,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I still know how to drive it,
but I've lost my self-confidence.</b></font>

100
00:07:24,284 --> 00:07:29,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I feel so confused, even panicky.</b></font>

101
00:07:34,134 --> 00:07:36,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Open 24 Hours"</b></font>

102
00:07:39,304 --> 00:07:42,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry, Itsuki. Making you drive
all the way out here to Saitama...</b></font>

103
00:07:42,704 --> 00:07:47,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nah, it's a lot closer from
Shibukawa to here than I thought!</b></font>

104
00:07:47,004 --> 00:07:51,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you think about it,
Saitama and Gunma are neighbors!</b></font>

105
00:07:51,244 --> 00:07:54,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A bit of a trip on the trains, maybe,
but close by if you're in a car.</b></font>

106
00:07:54,484 --> 00:07:57,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really? Then I'm glad.</b></font>

107
00:07:57,014 --> 00:08:02,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So don't you hesitate to call me
any time! I'm always free at night.</b></font>

108
00:08:02,854 --> 00:08:04,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll come out here lickety-split!</b></font>

109
00:08:04,994 --> 00:08:07,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki, don't you have a girlfriend?</b></font>

110
00:08:07,334 --> 00:08:10,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, of course I don't...</b></font>

111
00:08:23,214 --> 00:08:26,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>K-Kazumi!</b></font>

112
00:08:26,614 --> 00:08:29,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You have a boyfriend?</b></font>

113
00:08:29,454 --> 00:08:31,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I...</b></font>

114
00:08:32,524 --> 00:08:35,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unfortunately, no.</b></font>

115
00:08:35,094 --> 00:08:37,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For real?! I'm so glad!</b></font>

116
00:08:37,524 --> 00:08:41,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>N-No! I mean, uh, I don't mean
anything weird by that!</b></font>

117
00:08:41,034 --> 00:08:43,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry, gotta c-calm myself...</b></font>

118
00:08:45,104 --> 00:08:48,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You haven't changed at all, Itsuki.</b></font>

119
00:08:48,374 --> 00:08:52,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I get that all the time. "You aren't
makin' any progress at all."</b></font>

120
00:08:52,144 --> 00:08:55,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, that's not what I meant.</b></font>

121
00:08:55,214 --> 00:08:59,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're probably the type who
can't keep things hidden, huh?</b></font>

122
00:08:59,484 --> 00:09:02,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I get <i>that</i> a lot, too. What I
think goes straight to my face.</b></font>

123
00:09:02,814 --> 00:09:07,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think that's a good thing. Like there
are no secret agendas or anything.</b></font>

124
00:09:07,424 --> 00:09:10,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It feels comfortable to be around you.</b></font>

125
00:09:10,894 --> 00:09:15,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Uh, well, I've always been like this.</b></font>

126
00:09:15,564 --> 00:09:17,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't really get it myself!</b></font>

127
00:09:20,264 --> 00:09:23,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you very much!</b></font>

128
00:09:24,604 --> 00:09:27,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, I still don't really understand.</b></font>

129
00:09:27,844 --> 00:09:29,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For someone with Takumi's skills,</b></font>

130
00:09:29,674 --> 00:09:35,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it shouldn't be that hard to get as good
at four-wheel drive as he has at rear-wheel.</b></font>

131
00:09:35,484 --> 00:09:39,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe he's talking on a level that's
impossible for us to understand.</b></font>

132
00:09:41,324 --> 00:09:43,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There's only one thing I do know:</i></b></font>

133
00:09:43,964 --> 00:09:50,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Bunta's curriculum of training and driving</i>
<i>techniques has just entered a new phase.</i></b></font>

134
00:09:54,704 --> 00:09:56,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Say, Kazumi...</b></font>

135
00:09:56,004 --> 00:10:00,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you mind if we swing by the pass where
Takumi and Wataru raced the other day?</b></font>

136
00:10:00,544 --> 00:10:04,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd like to race that course in my own car.</b></font>

137
00:10:04,444 --> 00:10:07,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure. But that one's pretty difficult.</b></font>

138
00:10:07,684 --> 00:10:12,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yup. And challenging it is what makes a man!</b></font>

139
00:10:22,194 --> 00:10:24,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This takes a lot of steering work...</b></font>

140
00:10:24,504 --> 00:10:27,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't really tell where the lines are!</b></font>

141
00:10:30,374 --> 00:10:33,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow! Sure enough, that's turbo tuning for you!</b></font>

142
00:10:46,054 --> 00:10:51,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And sudden turbo boosts. This reminds me</i>
<i>of how my brother's Levin used to run.</i></b></font>

143
00:10:56,834 --> 00:11:00,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is hard... It's so different from Akina.</b></font>

144
00:11:00,504 --> 00:11:01,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I couldn't run it at all.</b></font>

145
00:11:01,874 --> 00:11:08,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You say that, but you've really gotten good!
I feel safe riding next to you.</b></font>

146
00:11:08,244 --> 00:11:11,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, well! I've been practicing a lot!</b></font>

147
00:11:11,884 --> 00:11:16,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My turbo's got its own quirks,
so I've gotta practice.</b></font>

148
00:11:47,954 --> 00:11:51,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Dammit! It's no good...</i></b></font>

149
00:12:01,134 --> 00:12:04,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi? He said that?</b></font>

150
00:12:04,064 --> 00:12:06,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh. You don't say.</b></font>

151
00:12:06,164 --> 00:12:08,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't give me that "You don't say."</b></font>

152
00:12:08,434 --> 00:12:11,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you planning this time?</b></font>

153
00:12:11,144 --> 00:12:16,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, well... That's a long story,
so I'll leave out the specifics.</b></font>

154
00:12:16,114 --> 00:12:21,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The point is, I'm gonna have him experience
the awesome capabilities of more modern cars.</b></font>

155
00:12:21,114 --> 00:12:27,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're doing that now? Takumi's already
done plenty of racing against modern cars.</b></font>

156
00:12:27,454 --> 00:12:29,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, but he doesn't <i>know</i> them.</b></font>

157
00:12:29,994 --> 00:12:33,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As a driver, he's specialized
only in the Eight-Six.</b></font>

158
00:12:35,864 --> 00:12:39,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He says he doesn't know how
to drive the Eight-Six anymore...</b></font>

159
00:12:39,934 --> 00:12:42,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But the truth is, that shouldn't be the case.</b></font>

160
00:12:42,634 --> 00:12:45,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Meaning?</b></font>

161
00:12:45,104 --> 00:12:49,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not the driving of it, but the
Eight-Six itself he's lost hope in,</b></font>

162
00:12:49,174 --> 00:12:53,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but he doesn't wanna acknowledge that,
so he's just comin' up with excuses.</b></font>

163
00:12:53,314 --> 00:12:55,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still, this is just as I'd planned.</b></font>

164
00:12:55,684 --> 00:13:00,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, don't tell me you're trying to force
him from the Eight-Six to the Impreza!</b></font>

165
00:13:00,284 --> 00:13:04,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wouldn't do that. That's <i>my</i> car.</b></font>

166
00:13:04,894 --> 00:13:11,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think this is gonna take a bit of time.
But he's gonna have to work through it.</b></font>

167
00:13:23,144 --> 00:13:24,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mogi...</i></b></font>

168
00:13:24,714 --> 00:13:27,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I wonder what she's doing these days.</i></b></font>

169
00:13:27,754 --> 00:13:31,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I bet she's not lonely at all, though.</i></b></font>

170
00:13:31,854 --> 00:13:34,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've been so busy and stressed out with D</i></b></font>

171
00:13:34,424 --> 00:13:38,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>that it's like I've been charging forward</i>
<i>with no time to think of anything else.</i></b></font>

172
00:13:38,524 --> 00:13:45,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I wonder if I'm losing steam.</i>
<i>I sure am thinking about her a lot.</i></b></font>

173
00:13:45,164 --> 00:13:48,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Why do I feel this lonely?</i></b></font>

174
00:14:06,954 --> 00:14:10,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Up to this point, it's not all that different...</b></font>

175
00:14:12,024 --> 00:14:13,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But here!</b></font>

176
00:14:13,394 --> 00:14:15,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is where it all changes.</b></font>

177
00:14:18,604 --> 00:14:23,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't believe it! Even in the rain...</i></b></font>

178
00:14:23,034 --> 00:14:25,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...there's such a sense of stability.</i></b></font>

179
00:14:33,484 --> 00:14:38,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So this cousin of mine living in Higashi
Matsuyama drives this silver Altezza</b></font>

180
00:14:38,424 --> 00:14:42,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and let me drive it one time,
and it's <i>such</i> an awesome car!</b></font>

181
00:14:42,894 --> 00:14:45,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An Altezza, huh? Sure is.</b></font>

182
00:14:49,234 --> 00:14:50,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh? Aren't you going to answer?</b></font>

183
00:14:50,934 --> 00:14:54,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, it's nothing important.</b></font>

184
00:14:55,904 --> 00:15:00,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hm! She doesn't want anyone</i>
<i>to butt in on our private date!</i></b></font>

185
00:15:00,444 --> 00:15:02,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, goddammit!</b></font>

186
00:15:02,244 --> 00:15:04,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How long're you gonna keep us waitin'?!</b></font>

187
00:15:06,184 --> 00:15:08,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Move your ass, register boy!</b></font>

188
00:15:08,284 --> 00:15:09,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm very sorry for the wait, sir.</b></font>

189
00:15:09,984 --> 00:15:12,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um, will this be all together or...</b></font>

190
00:15:12,154 --> 00:15:14,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're payin' separate, of course, dipshit!</b></font>

191
00:15:24,664 --> 00:15:26,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Those guys just now drive Lancer Evos...</b></font>

192
00:15:26,934 --> 00:15:28,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Say, Itsuki.</b></font>

193
00:15:28,834 --> 00:15:32,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Will you let me drive your Levin a little bit?</b></font>

194
00:15:32,944 --> 00:15:36,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have a license but no car, so if I don't
get behind the wheel once in a while,</b></font>

195
00:15:36,444 --> 00:15:39,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm worried I'll forget how to drive.</b></font>

196
00:15:39,044 --> 00:15:41,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure thing. Of course!</b></font>

197
00:15:41,514 --> 00:15:44,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can be your coach!</b></font>

198
00:15:55,294 --> 00:15:56,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What do I do?</i></b></font>

199
00:15:56,564 --> 00:16:00,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>How can I race so that this</i>
<i>car won't lose to my dad's?</i></b></font>

200
00:16:05,844 --> 00:16:09,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The more I drive, the more I don't know.</i></b></font>

201
00:16:20,524 --> 00:16:25,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What a screwup. How many years</i>
<i>has it been since I've spun out?</i></b></font>

202
00:16:30,094 --> 00:16:35,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No matter how I look at it, it's no use.</i>
<i>The Eight-Six can't beat that car.</i></b></font>

203
00:16:44,744 --> 00:16:52,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I thought I'd been giving it my all up till now,</i>
<i>but I'll have to go one step further.</i></b></font>

204
00:16:52,024 --> 00:16:56,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm going to have to squeeze every</i>
<i>ounce out of this car's potential.</i></b></font>

205
00:16:56,454 --> 00:17:02,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If I can't, then I don't have what it</i>
<i>takes to be a driver in Project D.</i></b></font>

206
00:17:13,404 --> 00:17:17,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You again? If you're looking
for Kazumi, she's not here.</b></font>

207
00:17:17,114 --> 00:17:21,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, really? Do you mind if I wait?</b></font>

208
00:17:21,454 --> 00:17:25,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have to meet with her...
speak with her one more time.</b></font>

209
00:17:25,724 --> 00:17:29,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Otherwise, I think this regret
will never go away.</b></font>

210
00:17:28,824 --> 00:17:31,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Tea""Boxed Lunches"</b></font>

211
00:17:31,164 --> 00:17:35,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Sweets Fair""Original Cakes"</b></font>

212
00:17:35,634 --> 00:17:38,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh? It's my brother.</b></font>

213
00:17:39,264 --> 00:17:41,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello?</b></font>

214
00:17:45,844 --> 00:17:51,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you know what kind of a position
that puts me in? Just say, "Leave."</b></font>

215
00:17:51,444 --> 00:17:55,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't care. I'm hanging up now.</b></font>

216
00:17:55,014 --> 00:17:57,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is it? Is everything all right at home?</b></font>

217
00:17:57,784 --> 00:18:00,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, it's nothing.</b></font>

218
00:18:12,934 --> 00:18:16,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unbelievable. Itsuki's been
on a date since this morning...</b></font>

219
00:18:16,974 --> 00:18:20,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but I have to go out on a
Saturday drive with your ass.</b></font>

220
00:18:20,474 --> 00:18:23,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, back at you.</b></font>

221
00:18:23,114 --> 00:18:24,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is it?</b></font>

222
00:18:24,814 --> 00:18:29,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At that convenience store just now,
wasn't that Itsuki's Levin?</b></font>

223
00:18:29,784 --> 00:18:34,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The little bugger's going on a date
around here, is he? All right!</b></font>

224
00:18:37,394 --> 00:18:39,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Something seems a little off.</b></font>

225
00:18:39,324 --> 00:18:42,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, kind of awkward somehow.</b></font>

226
00:18:42,334 --> 00:18:46,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you say we head back?
I can take you most of the way there.</b></font>

227
00:18:48,534 --> 00:18:50,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I...</b></font>

228
00:18:50,304 --> 00:18:53,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't want to go home tonight.</b></font>

229
00:18:56,544 --> 00:18:58,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>D-Did you hear that just now, Iketani?!</b></font>

230
00:18:58,744 --> 00:19:04,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It can't be! The line that
every man wants to hear!</b></font>

231
00:19:04,154 --> 00:19:06,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Iketani!</b></font>

232
00:19:06,684 --> 00:19:09,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>She doesn't want to go home?! So that means...</i></b></font>

233
00:19:09,554 --> 00:19:12,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Oh! Her face, so deep in thought...</i></b></font>

234
00:19:12,364 --> 00:19:14,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It must be that!</i></b></font>

235
00:19:18,864 --> 00:19:24,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>S-So right now, you and me...</b></font>

236
00:19:24,944 --> 00:19:26,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's go get a room!!</b></font>

237
00:19:26,204 --> 00:19:27,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shock and awe!!</b></font>

238
00:19:27,744 --> 00:19:29,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>H-He said it!</b></font>

239
00:19:29,274 --> 00:19:33,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no way it could
go that smoothly, though.</b></font>

240
00:19:33,114 --> 00:19:35,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's gotta be some turn of--</b></font>

241
00:19:35,284 --> 00:19:37,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

242
00:19:39,454 --> 00:19:43,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey! Hey, pull yourself together, Iketani!</b></font>

243
00:19:43,054 --> 00:19:44,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But...</b></font>

244
00:19:44,924 --> 00:19:49,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Before we do, there's
something I want to tell you.</b></font>

245
00:19:49,734 --> 00:19:53,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not here. Let's go over there.</b></font>

246
00:19:58,374 --> 00:20:01,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um, I'll be honest...</b></font>

247
00:20:01,614 --> 00:20:07,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was dating someone up
until about a month ago.</b></font>

248
00:20:10,154 --> 00:20:15,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think I still haven't gotten over him.</b></font>

249
00:20:15,924 --> 00:20:21,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But going forward, you and I can get closer,</b></font>

250
00:20:21,234 --> 00:20:24,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and I think I can forget about that other guy.</b></font>

251
00:20:24,234 --> 00:20:29,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you can accept that...</b></font>

252
00:20:29,274 --> 00:20:31,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...then I can be with you.</b></font>

253
00:20:34,914 --> 00:20:39,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um, when you said you were "dating" him,</b></font>

254
00:20:39,014 --> 00:20:44,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess you two got rooms in hotels and stuff.</b></font>

255
00:20:51,524 --> 00:20:56,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd like to ask one more thing.
About how many times?</b></font>

256
00:20:56,294 --> 00:20:59,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Like, more than ten? Or maybe less?</b></font>

257
00:21:01,274 --> 00:21:04,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Probably... more, I think.</b></font>

258
00:21:08,844 --> 00:21:14,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Suck it up, Itsuki! I know it's</i>
<i>a shock, but hang in there!</i></b></font>

259
00:21:14,144 --> 00:21:18,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki, do you hate me now?</b></font>

260
00:21:18,124 --> 00:21:21,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>N-No, I don't, but...</b></font>

261
00:21:38,804 --> 00:21:41,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I finally found you.</b></font>

262
00:21:44,344 --> 00:21:45,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wataru.</b></font>

263
00:21:45,744 --> 00:21:48,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's go, Itsuki. There's no
reason to stick around here.</b></font>

264
00:21:48,854 --> 00:21:52,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kazumi, wait. You can't just run away.</b></font>

265
00:21:52,184 --> 00:21:54,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This has got nothing to do with you!</b></font>

266
00:21:54,654 --> 00:21:57,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sayin' I don't like cowards.</b></font>

267
00:21:57,524 --> 00:22:01,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you've got nothing to feel guilty about,
then don't go hangin' up on people!</b></font>

268
00:22:01,564 --> 00:22:05,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kazumi, won't you listen to what I have to say?</b></font>

269
00:22:05,104 --> 00:22:09,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can't suddenly say something like
that to me. Don't bother me anymore!</b></font>

270
00:22:09,834 --> 00:22:13,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want you to hear this.
I want to get back together.</b></font>

271
00:22:15,014 --> 00:22:22,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's a reason I've been
acting so indecisive toward you.</b></font>

272
00:22:22,084 --> 00:22:24,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wasn't confident.</b></font>

273
00:22:24,784 --> 00:22:31,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm just a normal, plain old office worker.
Plus there's the age difference...</b></font>

274
00:22:31,524 --> 00:22:33,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought there was no way</b></font>

275
00:22:33,294 --> 00:22:37,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>a young girl would want to hang
out with someone like me forever.</b></font>

276
00:22:37,094 --> 00:22:40,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It'd just be a matter of
time before she left me...</b></font>

277
00:22:40,434 --> 00:22:44,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So I acted like this was a game.</b></font>

278
00:22:44,534 --> 00:22:47,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But that's not how I really feel.</b></font>

279
00:22:47,544 --> 00:22:53,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Being away from you, I learned full
well how important you are to me.</b></font>

280
00:22:53,314 --> 00:22:56,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kazumi, I need you.</b></font>

281
00:22:56,784 --> 00:22:58,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What the hell's with this guy?!</i></b></font>

282
00:22:58,654 --> 00:23:01,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He shows up out of nowhere</i>
<i>and starts talking shit.</i></b></font>

283
00:23:01,284 --> 00:23:05,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Right now, she and I are in love!</i></b></font>

284
00:23:05,324 --> 00:23:07,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki...</b></font>

285
00:23:07,664 --> 00:23:11,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you waiting for?
There's no reason to hold back.</b></font>

286
00:23:11,604 --> 00:23:14,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just go with how you feel.</b></font>

287
00:23:14,734 --> 00:23:20,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Run to the chest of the
man you really care for!</b></font>

288
00:23:20,304 --> 00:23:24,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki... Yeah, you're right.</b></font>

289
00:23:33,854 --> 00:23:35,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, that backfired.</b></font>

290
00:23:35,294 --> 00:23:37,484
